abstract: |
    Workspace Wiki is a Visual Studio Code extension that scans your workspace for documentation files (Markdown and plain text by default, fully customizable) and presents them in a sidebar tree view for fast preview and editing. It emphasizes readability, predictable ordering (README/index handling, alphabetical directories), and easy access via preview or edit. All operations are local-first and privacy-friendly.
